## Sprint 2 - Analysis & Diagrams (21.10 - 4.11)

### Meeting Date: 21.10
**Topic:** Use Cases & Constraints

#### Completed Tasks
- [x] Use Case Diagram - Visual Paradigm
- [x] Καταγραφή περιορισμών
- [x] Οικονομική Βιωσιμότητα

#### What We Did
- **al:** Created comprehensive Use Case Diagram in Visual Paradigm
- **gi:** Documented regulatory, operational, and technical constraints
- **vp, af:** Analyzed economic viability and ROI projections

#### Decisions Made
- Confirmed GDPR compliance as mandatory requirement
- Decided to host data within EU using Azure
- Established that cost reduction is primary economic benefit

### Meeting Date: 28.10
**Topic:** Current State Analysis

#### Completed Tasks
- [x] Ανάλυση Υφιστάμενης Κατάστασης & Διαδικασιών
- [x] Καταγραφή τρέχουσας ροής - BPMN
- [x] Root Cause Analysis
- [x] SWOT Analysis

#### What We Did
- **af, al:** Modeled current ("as-is") processes using BPMN
- **Team:** Conducted interviews with municipal employees
- **gi:** Performed root cause analysis identifying key pain points
- **vp:** Led SWOT analysis session

#### Challenges & Blockers
- Current processes are poorly documented and inconsistent
- Manual workflows lead to errors and lack of traceability

#### Notes
- Current state relies on outdated Excel sheets and verbal agreements
- Major opportunity to digitize and standardize processes

### Meeting Date: 4.11
**Topic:** Future State Design

#### Completed Tasks
- [x] Σχεδίαση Στόχου ("to-be") & Μετρικές Επιτυχίας
- [x] Ορισμός στόχων SMART
- [x] Μετρικές - KPIs
- [x] Κριτήρια Αποδοχής

#### What We Did
- **Team:** Designed target ("to-be") state with improved workflows
- **vp:** Defined SMART goals for each major objective
- **gi:** Established KPIs for measuring success
- **af:** Created acceptance criteria for system validation

#### Decisions Made
- Target uptime: ≥ 99%
- Resource utilization goal: ≥ 90%
- Request completion time: < 3 days

