- [x] Έλεγχοι
- [x] Κατηγορίες Δοκιμών
- [x] Πίνακας Ιχνηλασιμότητας
- [x] Δοκιμές & Αποδοχή (User Acceptance Testing - UAT)

#### What We Did
- **al:** Created detailed user flow diagrams for all user types
- **al:** Designed mockup screens for municipality dashboard, citizen portal, and admin console
- **af:** Defined testing categories (unit, integration, E2E, performance, security)
- **gi:** Created traceability matrix linking requirements to tests
- **vp:** Planned UAT approach with municipal employees and citizens

#### Decisions Made
- Prioritize mobile-first responsive design
- Ensure WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility compliance
- Use Angular Material for consistent UI components

#### Notes
- Mockups received positive initial feedback from team
- Need to validate with actual users during pilot phase

